acau, where players are chasing a US$2 million (S$2.7 million) prize fund and all-important ranking points.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 625, \"end\": 636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rahul_Singh_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.8695651579046557, \"rank\": 0.12166666666667184, \"text\": \"Rahul Singh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rahul_Singh_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rahul_Singh_(actor)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this week's International Series Macau\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 697}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"a US$2 million (S$2.7 million) prize fund\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"all-important ranking points\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 799}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only 60 men's players will reach Paris 2024 and, with most countries having a maximum of two places, competition is fierce before the Olympic Golf Rankings (OGR) are finalised in June.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 835, \"end\": 845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 2.2579253834288156e-13, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 959, \"end\": 962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GDAL\", \"score\": 0.8853743156552112, \"rank\": 0.12946578900915548, \"text\": \"OGR\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GDAL\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GDAL\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only 60 men's players\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"most countries\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"a maximum\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \"two places\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Golf Rankings\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Saudi-bankrolled LIV Golf has invested US$300 million in the Asian Tour - which, unlike LIV, receives world-ranking points - leading to the creation of the International Series.\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1005, \"end\": 1013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LIV Golf\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\"}, {\"begin\": 1049, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Tour\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0572021254844203e-28, \"text\": \"Asian Tour\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Tour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Tour\"}, {\"begin\": 1076, \"end\": 1079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_LIV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4427750097388758e-18, \"text\": \"LIV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_LIV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_LIV\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"world-ranking points\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"the creation\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1136}, {\"ngram\": \"the International Series\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1164}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than 20 LIV golfers have made the short trip over from Hong Kong for this week's event at the Macau Golf and Country Club, and Singh agreed many have ranking points on their minds.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1180, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_LIV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4427750097388758e-18, \"text\": \"LIV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedi